name: THE LIMINAL SPACE : THE FLICKERS
description:
THE LIMINAL SPACE : THE FLICKERS is part of an ongoing series of THE LIMINAL SPACE I have been developing for quite awhile. 

Liminal space exists when physical experience meets the internal dialogue. An ever evolving space for one to comprehend the present time and its embodiment in many forms. 

THE LIMINAL SPACE : THE FLICKERS explored the immediacy of time and movements in order to be present.
